@startuml FeatG40_GetAlertHistory
title FeatG40 - Get Alert History Flow

actor User
participant UI
participant GetAlertHistoryEndpoint
participant MediatR
participant GetAlertHistoryHandler
participant Repository
database Database

User -> UI: 1. GET /alerts/history\n(pageNumber, pageSize)
UI -> GetAlertHistoryEndpoint: 2. GET /api/v1/alerts/history
GetAlertHistoryEndpoint -> GetAlertHistoryEndpoint: 3. Extract JWT user ID

alt User NOT authenticated
    GetAlertHistoryEndpoint --> UI: 4. 401 Unauthorized
else User authenticated
    GetAlertHistoryEndpoint -> MediatR: 5. Send(GetAlertHistoryRequest)
    MediatR -> GetAlertHistoryHandler: 6. Handle(request)

    GetAlertHistoryHandler -> Repository: 7. Get notification logs\nby user ID
    Repository -> Database: 8. SELECT NotificationLogs\nWHERE UserId = ?
    Database --> Repository: 9. NotificationLogs
    Repository --> GetAlertHistoryHandler: 10. List<NotificationLog>

    GetAlertHistoryHandler -> Repository: 11. Get paginated AlertIds\n(latest first)
    Repository -> Database: 12. SELECT DISTINCT AlertId\nORDER BY CreatedAt SKIP TAKE
    Database --> Repository: 13. Paginated AlertIds
    Repository --> GetAlertHistoryHandler: 14. List<AlertId>

    GetAlertHistoryHandler -> Repository: 15. Get alerts with\nstation details
    Repository -> Database: 16. SELECT Alerts + Stations\nWHERE AlertId IN (?)
    Database --> Repository: 17. Alert details
    Repository --> GetAlertHistoryHandler: 18. List<Alert>

    GetAlertHistoryHandler -> GetAlertHistoryHandler: 19. Build AlertHistoryDto

    GetAlertHistoryHandler --> MediatR: 20. Response\n(success: true, data)
    MediatR --> GetAlertHistoryEndpoint: 21. Response
    GetAlertHistoryEndpoint --> UI: 22. 200 OK\n(alerts, pagination)
    UI --> User: 23. Display alert history
end

@enduml
